stories.title: Florida woman charged after allegedly attacking 72-year-old Trump supporter wearing MAGA hat
stories.preview: Laura Garrett, 33, is facing multiple charges after she allegedly attacked an elderly Trump supporter after confronting him for wearing a MAGA hat.
